    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent mechanical updates include a comprehensive Inspection II service and a subframe reinforcement check, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with confidence. Equipped with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, this example delivers the balanced, communicative handling these cars are known for. Minor cosmetic wear is present, but the performance envelope remains sharp and mechanically sound.",
